main event: Two unidentified objects were spotted in Spokane, Washington, changing shapes and colors over a period of time.
interesting points: The first object was described as round and appeared to oscillate like a pendulum., The second object changed from oblong to round and had a spider-web appearance when viewed through a telescope., Reports were made to the local police department for investigation., Observations lasted between one hour ten minutes to one hour twenty minutes., Observers included a reliable civilian patrolman and a military major.
witness description: one civilian patrolman and one military major
